      <title>Microchip Technology 預計季度業績將因庫存過剩影響而疲弱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microchip-technology-expects-weak-quarterly-results-excess-inventory-impact-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Microchip Technology週一預測第一季淨銷售額和利潤低於華爾街預期，顯示客戶繼續清理過剩庫存導致需求疲軟，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌超過4%。]]></description>
